site_title: Home - Storied Travel
site_description:
Storied Travel is an award-winning Boston-based travel agency with expert travel agents in Boston, Massachusetts, Seattle, Washington, and Charlotte, North Carolina, serving clients across all 50 states and internationally. Our dedicated travel agents specialize in crafting tailor-made luxury vacations designed to fit your unique preferences and budget—delivering unforgettable experiences without exceeding your investment.

We design once-in-a-lifetime African safari adventures in Tanzania, South Africa, and Kenya, along with immersive cultural journeys to Ghana, Portugal, Spain, Germany, France, the Netherlands, Italy, Greece, Peru, Iceland, Croatia, Turkey, Egypt, Japan, India, Vietnam, Colombia, Argentina, Chile, and the UAE (Dubai & Abu Dhabi).

Looking for a relaxing beach escape, adventure-filled hiking expedition, rainforest retreat, or wellness getaway? We curate exclusive trips—including Ayurveda wellness retreats—to Costa Rica, the Dominican Republic, Panama, Mexico, India, Greece, Bali, Thailand, Jamaica, St. Kitts, the Bahamas, and Dominica.

Our expert travel agents design stress-free, VIP travel experiences for time-starved professionals, busy families, solo travelers, multi-generational groups, girls’ trips, honeymooners, and wellness seekers. We handle every detail, offering personalized service, insider access, and seamless planning—so all you have to do is pack your bags.

Discover the difference of working with an award-winning travel agency. Contact us today to start planning your next luxury vacation!
